data.description: 3,176 SF of living space per seller and plans! This sprawling acreage is truly a nature lover's paradise, offering unparalleled privacy. Property boasts abundant timber & pond at the back, creating serene & peaceful environment perfect for recreational activities/hunting. Log cabin vibes w/ custom woodwork adding rustic charm to every corner. Grand foyer has drop zone leading to dining space that flows to cozy family room w/ built-in nook under the staircase. Main level primary is truly a retreat w/ oversized walk-in closet fitted w/ barn doors & a luxurious ensuite w/ relaxing jet tub & walk-in shower. 2 addt'l BRs on the main w/ full BA. A bonus room perfect for an office, storage/playroom. This level also has a very functional laundry room w/ storage & mudroom leading to an oversized garage. The tailor-made kitchen is a show stopper w/ endless cabinets & countertops, large pantry, custom island, peninsula seating, pot filler & gas range. As you ascend the catwalk, you are afforded a breathtaking view of the main level. The huge rec/family room includes hidden storage & the perfect spot for entertainment/relaxation. Another full BA & 3 more large BRs complete this level. The large front yard is set away from the road creating an air of seclusion. The covered back patio provides a peaceful spot to enjoy the surrounding woods & ample wildlife. This property is a rare gem & a true escape from the hustle & bustle of everyday life! 13 Mo HWA Platinum Home Warranty included!
